<section class="community-people">
  <img class="section-badge" src="{{ "lp-community-section-badge-people.png" | file_url }}" alt="community people">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Get inspiring encouragement and support from people facing the same challenges as you</h2>
    <p>Welcome to the world's largest diabetes support group. We're so happy to have you. If you’ve ever felt alone on your diabetic journey, that ends now.<br><br>You’re now tapped into the #1 largest and most interconnected group of diabetics in the world. The most valueable tool for your diabetes self management. Here, you’re always heard and understood, and you always have the support you need.</p>
    <div class="posts swiper">
      <div class="swiper-wrapper">
        <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-people-post-1.png" | file_url }}" alt="community people post">
        <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-people-post-2.png" | file_url }}" alt="community people post">
        <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-people-post-3.png" | file_url }}" alt="community people post">
        <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-people-post-4.png" | file_url }}" alt="community people post">
        <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-people-post-5.png" | file_url }}" alt="community people post">
      </div>
      <div class="swiper-button-prev swiper-nav"></div>
      <div class="swiper-button-next swiper-nav"></div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/winningtype2diabetestogether/" target=”_blank”><button>Introduce Yourself</button></a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .community-people .post {
    border: 2px solid #FFC701;
  }
</style>

<script>
  peoplePostsSlider = new Swiper('.community-people .swiper', {
    slidesPerView: 1,
    spaceBetween: 20,
    watchSlidesVisibility: true,
    loop: false,
    grabCursor: true,
    slideToClickedSlide: true,
    navigation: {
      nextEl: '.community-people .swiper-button-next',
      prevEl: '.community-people .swiper-button-prev',
      disabledClass: 'disabled'
    },
    breakpoints: {
      640: {
        slidesPerView: 2,
      },
      991: {
        slidesPerView: 3,
      }
    }
  });
</script>